  caseId: Case_001
  title: The Missing Watch
  briefText: "Victor Hale was found dead in his study at 11:45 PM. His antique pocket
    watch is missing.\n\nThe wall clock stopped during a struggle \u2014 but the
    hour it froze on contradicts everything his assistant claims about that night.\n\nSearch
    the scene. Find the evidence. Expose the lie."
